Package communication.messages

In this package are located all classes which represents main messages and responses for TCP communication between control and agent programs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgentMessage
    Represents task message for agent
    InvalidOperationResponse
    Represents invalid response from agent
    PhysicalMachineOperationMessage
    Represents kinf of physical machine operation message sent to agents
    VirtualMachineOperationMessage
    Represents kif of virtual machine operation message sent to agents
